CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FChannel Island regulators have forced
OL,7,FJersey Telecom (JT) to speed up its
OL,8,Fwork to allow phone number transfers
OL,9,Fto Coop Mobile following a backlash
OL,10,Ffrom its customers and competitors.
OL,12,FThe Jersey Competition Regulatory
OL,13,FAuthority (JCRA) says it received
OL,14,Fofficial complaints from the Channel
OL,15,FIslands Co-op and Sure, which provides
OL,16,FCoop Mobile's network infrastructure,
OL,17,Fas JT customers are unable to port
OL,18,Ftheir mobile numbers to the new
OL,19,Fprovider.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FThe Chief Executive Officer of the
OL,7,FChannel Islands Co-op, Mark Cox, has
OL,8,Fcalled the issue "disappointing" and
OL,9,Fadded that "we don't believe this
OL,10,Fdelay is reasonable".
OL,12,FThe Chief Executive Officer of Sure
OL,13,FGroup, Alistair Beak, explained: "Sure
OL,14,Fand JT customers can move between
OL,15,Fthose networks without losing their
OL,16,Fnumber but despite having ample time
OL,17,Fand successfully testing the process,
OL,18,FJT has not enabled number porting to
OL,19,Fand from the Co-op network."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FHowever, a JT spokesperson said
OL,7,Fswitching numbers to Sure is more
OL,8,Fstraightforward as "they use the same
OL,9,Funderlying infrastructure".
OL,11,FThey added that the porting process
OL,12,Fbetween JT and Coop Mobile involves
OL,13,Fseparate networks and is "complex",
OL,14,Falthough they are in the final stages
OL,15,Fof a "significant upgrade", which
OL,16,Fremains "a top operational priority".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FNow, the JCRA and the Guernsey
OL,7,FCompetition and Regulatory Authority
OL,8,F(GCRA) have said that under JT's
OL,9,Foriginal plans, the required changes
OL,10,Fwould not have been complete before
OL,11,FMay.
OL,13,FIn a joint statement, the regulators
OL,14,Fstate they have secured a
OL,15,F"significantly accelerated delivery"
OL,16,Ftimeline from the mobile service
OL,17,Fprovider, which will allow customers
OL,18,Fto transfer their numbers by Tuesday
OL,19,F17 March.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FIt reads: "MNP (Mobile Number
OL,7,FPortability) allows customers to
OL,8,Fswitch providers while keeping their
OL,9,Fexisting number, a key driver of
OL,10,Fcompetition and consumer choice.
OL,12,F"The revised timetable follows focused
OL,13,Faction by the JCRA and GCRA to resolve
OL,14,Fthe commercial dispute, understand
OL,15,Fdelivery barriers and press for a
OL,16,Ffaster resolution that better serves
OL,17,Fislanders.
OL,26,@nD@PpmoD@Lpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,F"JT has also given firm commitment
OL,7,Fthat all necessary work will be
OL,8,Fcompleted as quickly as possible.
OL,9,FContinued coordination between
OL,10,Foperators will remain essential to
OL,11,Fensure the new deadline is met.
OL,13,F"The JCRA and GCRA have welcomed the
OL,14,Frevised schedule and JT's commitment
OL,15,Fto expedite progress but remain
OL,16,Fdisappointed that regulatory
OL,17,Finvolvement was required."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FThe regulatory heads in both islands,
OL,7,FTim Ringsdore from Jersey and Michael
OL,8,FByrne from Guernsey, agree that
OL,9,Fallowing customers to keep their
OL,10,Fexisting numbers is a "critical
OL,11,Fcomponent of effective competition" in
OL,12,Fthe Channel Islands.
OL,14,FIn the UK, being able to switch phone
OL,15,Fnumbers between providers is a
OL,16,Frequirement governed by OFCOM - the
OL,17,FUK's regulator for communication
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
