PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772485564
OL,3,CRegulators force phone network to
OL,4,Cspeed up number transfer service
OL,6,FThis means that customers there can
OL,7,Fswitch mobile networks and keep their
OL,8,Fexisting number or get a new one by
OL,9,Fusing a free PAC or STAC code
OL,10,Frespectively.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/8
